name: TNO and Centaur Diameters, Albedos, and Densities - Documents
abstract: This data set is a compilation of published diameters, albedos, and densities for Transneptunian Objects (TNOs) and Centaurs. A total of 194 objects are listed, many with more than one entry. This version covers published values through 31 March 2018.
